OL,3,CThousands line the streets for parades
OL,4,Cmarking St Patrick's Day
OL,6,FSt Patrick's Day celebrations have
OL,7,Ftaken place across in Northern Ireland
OL,8,Fand the Republic of Ireland with
OL,9,Fthousands lining the streets in towns
OL,10,Fand cities for parades throughout the
OL,11,Fday.
OL,13,FIn Belfast, before the parade began,
OL,14,Fthousands of runners took part in the
OL,15,F10km race through the city's streets.
OL,17,FThe annual parade, led by Lord Mayor
OL,18,FTracy Kelly said the festivities are
OL,19,F"inclusive", "here for everybody" and
OL,20,F"what Belfast is all about".
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/5
