OL,3,CThousands line the streets for parades
OL,4,Cmarking St Patrick's Day
OL,6,FIn Downpatrick, the annual wreath
OL,7,Flaying service took place at St
OL,8,FPatrick's grave at Down Cathedral.
OL,10,FWhile in Dublin, large crowds gathered
OL,11,Fsince the early morning for the
OL,12,Flargest parade in Ireland.
OL,14,FThe procession comprising 12 large
OL,15,Ffloats and more than 3,000
OL,16,Fparticipants ran from Parnell Square
OL,17,Fin the north of the city, down
OL,18,FDublin's main thoroughfare, O'Connell
OL,19,FStreet, ending on the south side.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/5
