OL,3,CThousands line the streets for parades
OL,4,Cmarking St Patrick's Day
OL,6,FPresenter and podcaster Vogue
OL,7,FWilliams, who was the grand marshal of
OL,8,Fthis year's parade, said she could not
OL,9,Fsleep last night with the excitement.
OL,11,FIn Armagh, the ecclesiastical home of
OL,12,FSt Patrick, there was one of the
OL,13,Fbiggest spectacles of its kind in the
OL,14,Fcity.
OL,16,FIn Strabane, the town marked the 20th
OL,17,Fanniversary of its much-loved St
OL,18,FPatrick's Day parade featuring local
OL,19,Fschools, clubs and community groups as
OL,20,Fwell as bands and performers.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/5
